arge;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山，各自努力，不分化，不割蓆</span></span>"},{"pid":"04673a7e720b60258d22f90f26b43f6f6519f2be","tid":1267104,"uid":207904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T17:47:50.000Z","msg":"各位如果有情緒問題嘅話真係唔好收收埋埋，真係唔想再失去任何一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一個都不能少</span></span>"},{"pid":"ed282faa8079cb854841aacec7a1df90387f13c7","tid":1267104,"uid":213379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T17:48:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集合時間同地點</span></span><br />\n<br />\n&mdash; 唔 理 衝 唔 衝 ， 迫 爆 金 紫 荊 VER 2 &mdash;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1267041\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1267041</a>"},{"pid":"0d8166827a1402b24ae825f3e7bf5b3e56ef8721","tid":1267104,"uid":262435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T17:48:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f4ad8d3a6c966d07911062ab27d857fb44270124","tid":1267104,"uid":131686,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T17:48:39.000Z","msg":"食咗十幾粒催淚彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以後唔反唔屌00後了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64f1f7e15873418d94d0ae393804bed3d14744b6","tid":1267104,"uid":149435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T17:48:46.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86adab53562d3b13fe755280b51222465aa43246","tid":1